# This is a sample BMAD project. Unlike a real BMAD installation, we want to
# version-control the BMAD artifacts so reviewers and future readers can see
# the planning output side-by-side with the code. The repo-root `.gitignore`
# excludes `_bmad-output/` by default; we re-include it here.
!_bmad-output/
!_bmad-output/**
